CBRE Industrial and Logistics is pleased to present 10 Pritchard Road, Virginia for sale. 

The site features:

+ 3,799sqm* site (General Industry C) 
+ Improved with a 650sqm* high quality office /showroom 
+ Ample car parking onsite and rear lockable concrete hardstand 
+ Large hardstand area previously used as a display area
+ Secure site with fencing around the perimeter
+ Tenants in the immediate precinct include: Bunnings Warehouse, Sydney Tools, Beaumont Tiles, Petbarn, Chemist Warehouse, Rebel Sport & Officeworks. 
+ Prior to being the McCarthy Homes head office, the site was used as a nursery & timber/hardware centre 
+ Ideal location for medical or vet clinic (STCA)  
+ Lease in place to McCarthy Homes due to expire September 2021
+ Purchase as a going concern with holding income 

*Approx.

For more information please contact Dan Munnich and Dillon Murphy of CBRE.

CBRE are pleased to present 40 Telford Street, Virginia to the market For Lease or Sale.  

Key Features; 

•	Building will be modernised with architecturally designed new façade
•	Internal refurbishment works to the office will be completed 
•	Installation of two new wide electric roller doors 
•	1,982sqm Gross floor area 
•	1,523sqm clear span warehouse 
•	Separate workshop totalling 132sqm 
•	327sqm ground floor open plan office space 
•	Staff amenities including lunch room 
•	Building well positioned on site to allow for generous hardstand & container set down area 


Location 

40 Telford Street, Virginia is conveniently located just off major arterial Sandgate Road. The Brisbane Airport & Gateway Motorway are easily accessed via Toombul Road or the Tunnel Network. There is ample retail amenity along Sandgate & Robinson Roads. 


Phone Exclusive Agents CBRE for further information or to arrange an inspection today!

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: SOON TO BE REFURBISHED - FREESTANDING BUILDING WITH HARDSTAND
